{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"21ca09d3-da14-454d-a6a0-0022b2a8be4f","content":"Here's the recommended setup:\n\n**1. Project file (`MyTests.csproj`)** — MSTest.Sdk removes all boilerplate:\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.7.3\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n</Project>\n```\n\nThat's it — no `<PackageReference>` needed. The SDK brings in MSTest, the runner, and CodeCoverage automatically.\n\n**2. Enable parallel execution** — add a `.runsettings` file:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Parallelize>\n      <Workers>0</Workers>          <!-- 0 = one worker per core -->\n      <Scope>ClassLevel</Scope>     <!-- classes run in parallel -->\n    </Parallelize>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\nWire it up in the `.csproj` (or pass via CLI):\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n**3. Make database tests sequential** — use `[DoNotParallelize]`:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]                // runs sequentially, after all parallel tests finish\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Insert_Then_Query_ReturnsRow() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Delete_RemovesRow() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n| Concept | Mechanism |\n|---|---|\n| Parallel by default | `<Parallelize>` in `.runsettings` |\n| Scope options | `ClassLevel` (default) or `MethodLevel` |\n| Opt-out per class | `[DoNotParallelize]` attribute |\n| Worker count `0` | Auto-scales to CPU core count |\n\nClasses marked `[DoNotParallelize]` run **after** all parallel classes complete, ensuring no concurrent access to your database.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"20ebcb9b-abae-4c6c-85bf-e1ea7cfd1493","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The working directory is empty and there are no plugins to reference. Let me answer based on my knowledge of MSTest.Sdk.","outputTokens":578,"requestId":"602B:20684E:26165E4:28B3C95:6A03127F"},"id":"64770d05-eb39-450a-866d-381f5c1bbc07","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:44:16.873Z","parentId":"9f3661f1-808f-4cb6-a812-77a10e22595f"}
